io.janusproject.eclipse.buildpath

Class JanusClasspathContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sarl.eclipse.buildpath.AbstractSARLBasedClasspathContainer
      • io.janusproject.eclipse.buildpath.JanusClasspathContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jdt.core.IClasspathContainer

    public class JanusClasspathContainer
extends io.sarl.eclipse.buildpath.AbstractSARLBasedClasspathContainer
    Classpath container dedicated to the Janus platform.

    The Janus classpath library is an application library, i.e. it is included into the run-time classpath.
